{"type": "article", "id": 12625, "title": "智能健身手环", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-27T07:06:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060002159YMn1w5jvAab2Ice.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t台湾设计师颜文豪推出了一款智能健身手环，与现在市面上的健身手环相比，他在普通的可穿戴设备基础上加入了更加完备的硬件，用户可以根据运动项目的不同，现在佩戴在手腕上，脚腕等不同的部位。除此之外，手环还配备了一套算法，可以根据用户的健身数据提出专业的健身建议，承担私人健身教练的作用。这是<a href=\"http://welcome.moov.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>，点击可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140330h1flM07UnVRHtPTN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140331i2GwhaeoKQmLTC5X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140332wzULAT4MoRm0Gvh7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140332Ox2ewNuJXfEiTmrY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140333pW8LeZ0YqJ3iXkVH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}